7": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012773, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Out of those holy places which are on the way to Medina from Mecca like the graves of the martyrs of Fakh near Masjid-e-Taneem, grave of Abdullah bin Abbas in the Valley of Taif, the grave of Maimunah, the wife of the Holy Prophet (s) which is two farsakhs away from Mecca in Saraf, graves of Hawwa (s) in Jeddah and Aamena in Abawa, Masjid Ghadeer-e-Khum near Juhfah (two to three miles away from Juhfah), grave of Abu Zar-e-Ghiffari in Rabza, graves of the martyrs of Badr in Badr, grave of Abdullah bin Al-Harith bin Abdul Muttalib who was martyred while returning from the Battle of Badr due to severe wounds and is buried in Rawha which is 17 km. away from Medina.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Woh muqaddas ziyaraat jo Madina aur Makkeh ke darmiyaan hai, jaise keh Shohoda-e-Fakh jo Masjid-e-Taneem ke qareeb hai, Abdullah ibne Abbas ki qabr jo Waadi-e-Taif mein hai. Qabr-e-Maimunah, zauja-e-Rasool (s) jo Saraf, Makkeh se 2 farsakh ki duri par hai. Qabr-e-Hawwa (s) jo Jeddah mein hai aur Qabr-e-Aamena (s) jo Abawa mein hai. Masjid Ghadeer-e-Khum jo Juhfah se 2 ya 3 mile ki duri par hai. Qabr Abuzar-e-Ghiffaari jo Rabza mein hai, Qabr Shohoda-e-Badr jo Badr mein hai. Qabr-e-Abdullah bin Haaris bin Abdul Muttalib jo Badr se laut-te waqt shadeed zakhmi hone ki bina par shaheed huwe aur unki qabr Rawha jo Madine se 17 km. ki duri par hai.", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSig